*Zezaš* se oko njega. (You're teasing him.)
On *zeza* njega već neko vreme. (He's been teasing him for some time.)
On je već umoran od *zezanja*. (He's already tired of teasing.)
Ona ga je *zezala* zbog njegovog izgleda. (She teased him about his looks.)
Niko nije očekivao da će ona *zeza* njega. (Nobody expected her to tease him.)